Company Overview of VICIS, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
VICIS, Inc. designs and manufactures football helmets that mitigate linear and rotational impact forces. The company was formerly known as Spark Medical, Inc. and changed its name to VICIS, Inc. in May 2014. VICIS, Inc. was founded in 2013 and is based in Seattle, Washington.


