VICIS, Inc. Key Developments

VICIS Appoints Lisa Ertz as Advisor of VICIS Coalition and President of the VICIS Foundation
Jan 30 17
VICIS has added Lisa Ertz to its Coalition of advisors. Mother of NFL tight end Zach Ertz, Lisa brings an essential perspective to the VICIS Coalition. Lisa also takes on the role of president of the VICIS Foundation. As president, Lisa will work with corporations, athlete foundations, and other organizations interested in making financial contributions, as well as lead the selection of deserving schools and youth programs that will benefit from foundation grants.


