Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Leisure Products
Sub-Industry: Sporting Goods
Vicis, Inc. offers sporting goods. The Company designs and manufactures football helmets that mitigate linear and rotational impact forces. Vicis serves customers in the United States.




