WHAT IS THE MEDIA SAYING ABOUT VICIS? HERE IT IS.
We believe strongly in our mission and appreciate when the media shines light on what VICIS and others are doing to improve sports safety.  Because science has not yet established a correlation between impact force reduction and concussion risk, VICIS has made a point of refraining from making concussion-related claims. To the extent that the media may suggest we have developed a “concussion-proof” helmet or have otherwise amplified the benefits of the ZERO1, please recognize the data does not yet exist to support such a claim. Enjoy the articles, and please register on our Contact page to follow our progress. 
For media inquiries, please contact: vicis@barokas.com 







